{"id": "26528", "post": "<div class=\"post-26528 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-disaster-recovery tag-fire tag-germany tag-ovh tag-strasbourg\" id=\"post-26528\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/fire-destroys-ovhs-sbg-datacenter-strasbourg-germany/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Fire Destroys OVH\u2019s SBG Datacenter (Strasbourg, Germany)</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/disaster-recovery/\" rel=\"tag\">disaster recovery</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/fire/\" rel=\"tag\">fire</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/germany/\" rel=\"tag\">germany</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/ovh/\" rel=\"tag\">OVH</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/strasbourg/\" rel=\"tag\">strasbourg</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> March 10, 2021 @ 10:39 am, by raindog308</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ovh.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-26530 alignright litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ovh.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" align=\"right\" hspace=\"20\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ovh.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ovh-150x150.png.webp 150w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ovh.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/ovh-150x150.png.webp 150w\" data-was-processed=\"true\">OVH, one of the largest hosting providers in the world, suffered a runaway fire at their SBG datacenter in Strasbourg, Germany.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\"><em>We have a major incident on SBG2. The fire declared in the building. Firefighters were immediately on the scene but could not control the fire in SBG2. The whole site has been isolated which impacts all services in SGB1-4. We recommend to activate your Disaster Recovery Plan.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u2014 Octave Klaba (@olesovhcom) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/olesovhcom/status/1369478732247932929?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 10, 2021</a></p><p>According to further updates, SBG2 is completely destroyed and SBG1 is partly out of commission.&nbsp; No impact to SBG3 and SBG4, but as part of firefighting efforts, power has been shut down to the entire site so users are facing an extended outage and won\u2019t be restarted today.&nbsp; Fortunately, no injuries are reported.</p><p>Reuters has <a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-france-ovh-fire-idUSKBN2B20NU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">pictures</a> of the blaze.</p><p>OVH has 17 data centers in France and 32 worldwide.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div class=\"relpost-thumb-wrapper\"><div class=\"relpost-thumb-container\"><h3>Related posts:</h3><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-container\"><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/lowendtalk-2020-best-providers-award-results/\"><div style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"LowEndTalk 2020 Best Providers Award Results\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2020-top-providers-copy-150x150.png) no-repeat scroll 0% 0%; width: 150px; height: 150px;\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-single-text\" style=\"font-family: Arial;  font-size: 12px;  color: #333333;\">LowEndTalk 2020 Best Providers 